reviews.review_text:
84 auds Sound soooooo good.. why is that?

This is an excellent audience recording.. sounds like I'm right there 3rd row center stage all over again. Thank you Mr Taper!

Brent's Hammond B3 and rotating Leslie sound so fucking good on the build up to the end of Cold Rain & Snow .. his sound is just pushing the band.

I can't wait to dig into this aud more later...

The Drums > Space segments at these 1984 Red Rocks shows are a psychedelic dream come true.

And the Stella Blue is just downright spooky.. witchcraft was in the air that night..

"and when you hear that song, come crying like the night..."
